      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so i'm thinking about that character we were working on... the one who's basically a glitch in the system. i feel like they’ve just reached a point where they can't fight the erasure anymore. like, everything they ever did or felt is just being wiped out, and it feels... i don't know, empty. if they just let the deletion happen, does it even matter? like, is there any point in resisting if they're just going to be nothing anyway?",
