      "content": "but that struggle sounds so exhausting though. like, if the end result is just total nothingness regardless of how hard they fight, isn't the struggle just causing more unnecessary suffering? it feels like they're just prolonging the inevitable pain. wouldn't it be a relief to just... stop fighting it and let the silence happen?",
